channel.title: Help with Eclipse
channel.description:
[s]Hey so I've had eclipse for a while but I recently updated my JDK Version. now it wont work, heres the error. P.S. Already updated variables.
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/AxHX5.png[/img][/s]
EDIT: NVM, I fixed it, my jdk and eclipse didnt match, I had 86 bit jdk and x86 Eclipse.... Turns out I needed 64 bit :l
